    BlockContainer<GoloFunction>, ToplevelGoloElement

    public final class GoloFunction
extends ExpressionStatement<GoloFunction>
implements BlockContainer<GoloFunction>, ToplevelGoloElement
    Represents a function declaration.

    Such as 

    
 function foo = |x| -> x + 1

      • function

        public static GoloFunction function(java.lang.Object name)
        Creates a function declaration.

        Typical usage: 

        
 function("foo").withParameters("x").returns(plus(ReferenceLookup.of("x"), constant(1)))
        creates 
        
 function foo = |x| -> x + 1
